data.eml:eml: Description of two new and six known species of the genus Tylencholaimus de Man, 1876 (Nematoda: Dorylaimida) with a diagnostic compendium and key to species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Ahad, Sumaya, Ahmad, Wasim (2016): Description of two new and six known species of the genus Tylencholaimus de Man, 1876 (Nematoda: Dorylaimida) with a diagnostic compendium and key to species. Zootaxa 4107 (4): 451-490, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4107.4.1
